defines the harmonized set includes the no-topics baseline: a word \eqn{w}
is rare in document \eqn{j} if
\eqn{\min\bigl(\hat\pi_{\mathrm{glob}}(w),\, \min_K p^{K}_{jw}\bigr) < \tau_j,}{min(pi_glob(w), min_K p^K_jw) < tau_j,}
