\details{
OpTop indices (SE, Pearson \eqn{\chi^2}, and Deviance) are computed on the
fixed support \eqn{\{w \not\in C_j^*\} \cup \{\min\}} for each document,
where all words in \eqn{C_j^*} are collapsed into a single "\code{min}"
